descript.abstract: City boundaries for the nine-county Kansas City region. This data is produced in support for the 9-1-1 program through direct input by local governments. These boundaries are not split at county lines. For example, there is one polygon for Kansas City Missouri even though it spans four counties.
descript.purpose: General cartography, analysis, and feature identification.
